3\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/buying-guide-reviews/best-tvs-237003\"\u003e\u003cu\u003ebest TV’s\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, but it will do the trick for home projection.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-1920-80.png.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-1600-80.png.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-1280-80.png.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-1024-80.png.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-768-80.png.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-415-80.png.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-360-80.png.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-320-80.png.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY.png\" alt=\"Aldi hd led projector on pink background\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-1920-80.png 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-1600-80.png 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-1280-80.png 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-1024-80.png 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-768-80.png 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-415-80.png 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-360-80.png 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY-320-80.png 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY.png\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XdgWkYJ4waettVDGku5HoY.png\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Aldi)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAlongside bright, clear visuals, the Aldi projector is also very easy to set up. It’s USB supported, so all you need to do is plug it in and press play. It has an optional screen size so you can choose a range between 40 and 150 inches. It has both speakers and an earphone outlet if you’re enjoying the projector alone. It has a lamp life of 30,000 hours.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-mAwtWSKCAdpsTbzGDrruAR\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eNow, I haven’t had the chance to test the Aldi HD LED Projector, so I can’t vouch for how well it works. What I do know is that Aldi’s Specialbuy products constantly leave me impressed by their quality and value for money. However, if you’re not quite convinced, I’ve found three top-rated projectors that reviewers swear-by.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-id=\"f65a6890-0458-42df-b416-08ae8f8ca3dc\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=1599\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=idealhome-gb-7299553336802277967\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.currys.co.uk%2Fproducts%2Fepson-cow01-hd-ready-home-cinema-projector-10244447.html%3FistCompanyId%3Dbec25c7e-cbcd-460d-81d5-a25372d2e3d7%26istFeedId%3D4d7eb93e-055f-499d-8ee5-1cdcc50d67d1%26istItemId%3Drpqaqlplq%26istBid%3Dt\" data-model-name=\"Epson Co-W01 Hd Ready Home Cinema Projector\" data-url=\"https://www.currys.co.uk/products/epson-cow01-hd-ready-home-cinema-projector-10244447.html?istCompanyId=bec25c7e-cbcd-460d-81d5-a25372d2e3d7\u0026amp;istFeedId=4d7eb93e-055f-499d-8ee5-1cdcc50d67d1\u0026amp;istItemId=rpqaqlplq\u0026amp;istBid=t\" target=\"_blan